{Speech 6}{}{Another fool wandering around here.!\n}
{Speech 10}{}{Who are you?!}
{Speech 10 Answer 11}{}{My name is @pname@.}
{Speech 11}{}{If not for your help... I would have been killed. I'm in your debt.}
{Speech 11 Answer 12}{}{A little longer, and I might have been too late. }
{Speech 12}{}{Take this, as a token of my gratitude.}
{Speech 12 Answer 13}{}{Thanks, the money will come in handy.}
{Speech 13}{}{You've just been a great help to the Republic, @pname@. I'll ask Santiago to arrange a special night pass for you.}
{Speech 13 Answer Exit}{}{Thank you. [Leave]}
{Speech 14}{}{What? Another assassin?!}
{Speech 14 Answer Exit}{}{Wait, Westin, I...}
{Speech 20}{}{I don't give work to dung collectors and bums. Get out.}
{Speech 20 Answer Exit}{}{You're too cheeky, Westin. I'll teach you some manners. [Attack] }
{Speech 20 Answer 21}{}{I'm no bum.}
{Speech 21}{}{Clear off, @sex@|fool|fool|, before I call the guards.}
{Speech 21 Answer Exit}{}{I'm leaving. [Leave]}
{Speech 22}{}{I have no work for you.}
{Speech 22 Answer 23}{}{And if you think about it?}
{Speech 23}{}{I didn't invite you. If you don't get out right now, you'll be dealing with the guards.}
{Speech 24}{}{Oh, heavens! You again? How many times do I have to repeat it, I have no work.}
{Speech 24 Answer 25}{}{I thought you said "find me later".}
{Speech 25}{}{Wait. Have you ever been to Vault City?}
{Speech 25 Answer 27}{}{@sex@|I haven't|I haven't| been and don't plan to anytime soon.}
{Speech 25 Answer 26}{}{Of course. I hang out there all the time, my buddies run the local protection racket.}
{Speech 25 Answer 28}{}{I have. Why?}
{Speech 26}{}{What racket? What kind of talk is that? How tired I am of this wasteland scum...}
{Speech 26 Answer Exit}{}{What's that talk! Who are you calling scum, smartass!}
{Speech 27}{}{Then get out of here.}
{Speech 28}{}{If you want work so badly, then can you handle a simple task?}
{Speech 28 Answer 29}{}{Easy! What needs doing? Save the world? Enslave Vault City? Raise Tandi from the grave?}
{Speech 28 Answer 31}{}{Me, do something on the orders of a creep like you? Never in my life! [Leave]}
{Speech 28 Answer 30}{}{What needs to be done?}
{Speech 29}{}{Not funny. The Tandi joke was downright tasteless. Get lost. Guards!}
{Speech 29 Answer Exit}{}{I was just joking... I'm leaving...}
{Speech 30}{}{I'm running out of heart pills. You can't get them in the NCR. Only Vault City has them.}
{Speech 30 Answer 31}{}{Ha! You'll croak without your pills! Yes! It's the Lord's punishment! [Leave]}
{Speech 30 Answer 32}{}{Who in Vault City can I find these pills from?}
{Speech 31}{}{Go on, go. Don't linger, @sex@|idiot|fool|.}
{Speech 32}{}{My man was buying the pills from Helen Troy. And this week he was supposed to bring them. But something happened, and he's still not here.}
{Speech 32 Answer 33}{}{You want me to @sex@|find|find| your man? Or just buy the pills?}
{Speech 33}{}{I'll deal with my own people myself. What I need from you is to buy the pills and deliver them to me. When you return, I'll pay their full cost.}
{Speech 33 Answer 34}{}{How much will I get?}
{Speech 34}{}{Helen will ask 1000 caps for the medicine. Bring me the pills, and you'll get their cost, plus 1000 on top.}
{Speech 34 Answer 35}{}{Money up front! Otherwise I won't lift a finger!}
{Speech 34 Answer 36}{}{Money up front! Otherwise I won't lift a finger!}
{Speech 34 Answer Exit}{}{You can consider the pills already in your nightstand. [Leave]}
{Speech 34 Answer Exit*}{}{No, I don't have time to traipse off to the middle of nowhere for some idiotic pills. [Leave]}
{Speech 35}{}{Fine. But just try to cheat me, and you'll pay for it. I'll give you 1000, you'll get the rest when you come back to me.}
{Speech 35 Answer Exit}{}{I won't let you down. It's not my way. [Leave]}
